<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٤١٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو ثَوْر:</span> الْأَعْمَى.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> بِلَال.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> الشّعبِيّ , قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أرَاهُ الأول.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١٤١٤ - أَبُو ثَوْر.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عَطاء بن دِينَار.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> سُفْيَان الثَّوْريّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أخبرنَا خَيْثَمَة , ثَنَا إِسْحَاق , عَن عبد الرَّزَّاق ,<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عَن الثَّوْريّ , عَن أبي ثَوْر , عَن عَطاء بن دِينَار<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">أَن عمر رَضِي الله عَنهُ قَالَ:</span> لَا تعلمُوا رطانة<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>الْأَعَاجِم.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١٤١٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو ثَوْر:</span> الْحدانِي , قَبيلَة من<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>هَمدَان , كُوفِي.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> حُذَيْفَة.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو البخْترِي الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>١٤١٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو ثَعْلَبَة:</span> الْأَشْجَعِيّ. لَهُ صُحْبَة قَالَه البُخَارِيّ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>١٤١٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو ثَعْلَبَة:</span> الْخُشَنِي جرهم ,<span class="c5"> وَيُقَال:</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>جرثوم.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>أخبرنَا أَحْمد بن مهْرَان , ثَنَا مُوسَى بن زَكَرِيَّا ,<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>ثَنَا شباب الْعُصْفُرِي بِهَذَا.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>١٤١٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو ثَعْلَبَة:</span> ابْن عَم كردم , لَهُ<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>صُحْبَة.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> كردم بن قيس.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>١٤١٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو ثَعْلَبَة:</span> الْأنْصَارِيّ.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>أَن النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم قضى فِي سيل<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>مهروز.<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>رَوَاهُ حَمَّاد بن سَلمَة , عَن مُحَمَّد ابْن إِسْحَاق<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>عَنهُ.<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>١٤٢٠ - أَبُو ثروان.<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>رأى النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>رَوَاهُ عبد الْملك بن هَارُون بن عنترة , عَن أَبِيه<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>عَنهُ.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>١٤٢١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو ثُمَامَة:</span> مُحَمَّد بن مُسلم<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
